setSiteRestriction

public void setSiteRestriction(java.lang.String site)
This method is used to restrict the set of image search results returned by this searcher. To restrict to www.photobucket.com, simply call this method passing in a value of "www.photobucket.com". To clear site restrictions, pass in a value of null.
